data.description: **PRICE REDUCED** ** Looking for a low-maintenance home with a large yard, functional floorplan and lots of natural light? Here it is!  Full brick home with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, privacy fence, all on just under half an acre! Isolated Owner's Suite has separate closets, separate sinks, garden tub, and shower. Large family room with beautiful wood-burning fireplace and cathedral ceiling.  Large kitchen with breakfast nook and lots of cabinet space. Shelving in garage for extra storage. Large yard gives plenty of room for entertaining, gardening, or even adding a pool.
